{"tid":150423,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"太耐冇潛水想重溫下應該點做好","createTime":"2017-03-10T04:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T01:27:19.000Z","uid":30368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58df6b435877734276fd13cb50e8ca8daac7edfb","tid":150423,"uid":30368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:45:11.000Z","msg":"話說小弟上年考完個O仔之後就再冇潛過水,好多野都唔記得哂<br />\n呢排又心思思想重拾返<br />\n但係自己又冇技術用氣又快所以冇信心跟團出海,又未試過係香港潛水<br />\n想搵人教返我潛水,想問下爸打們有冇呢方面資料可以提供下?<br />\n我見上網有D單對單出海900蚊連租裝備咁樣樣既野,屌唔屌得過?<br />\n<br />\n見個網係咁<br />\n參加資格:持有水肺證書或以上資助歷咭的潛水員<br />\n課程大綱:一天出海實習,潛水主任或教練一次複習指導一次自修<br />\n費用<br />\n每人HK$800 (兩位或以上)<br />\n每人HK$900 單對單 <br />\n費用包括<br />\n船費<br />\n氣樽<br />\n午餐<br />\n教練費<br />\n全套潛水裝備<br />\n<br />\n麻煩咁多位爸絲比D意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341bb64fbe50dfcbab361a59e2487bae8f0bb5dd","tid":150423,"uid":30368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:46:31.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"15de152c45b41968daa1e52ee121bed240b6ac71","tid":150423,"uid":30368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:22:50.000Z","msg":"好後悔開係波台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推"},{"pid":"91cb469bb004d8edd70bdb9f1ebc90db38b89c7e","tid":150423,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T08:32:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好後悔開係波台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n推</blockquote><br />\n你好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n識唔識朋友有潛開水? 有就可以叫佢帶, 無就俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e091d427ded4bfb9429148a04fc502aea9abc063","tid":150423,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T08:36:44.000Z","msg":"賣下廣告先, 有個連登 + 高登潛水group, 有興趣e-mail揾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nwhite.glint@live.com"},{"pi